A Visual Novel Filled With Wacky Adventure and Romance!

Sweet Fuse: At Your Side stars Saki Inafune, niece to legendary game 
developer Keiji Inafune. Saki's famous uncle opens an amusement park and 
Saki attends the opening ceremony, but things really heat up when Count 
Hogstein, a malevolent pig, takes over the park, and holds everyone hostage.
Saki, along with seven sexy men, decides to enter Count Hogstein's deadly 
game in order to save her uncle and the other hostages. Will she be able 
to solve the complex puzzles that Count Hogstein and his merry henchmen 
have in store? And most importantly, which steamy bachelor will Saki choose?
